<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>[لام <span class="c2">(بنو)</span> :]<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>فخذ من بلحارث من بني شهر السراة بالسعودية.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(م)</span> عبد الله بن حميد: العرب ٩/ ٦٧<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
